Wannabeeism is the sincerest form of... what?  Trouble is, 99 % of those to whom wannabees expose themselves have no clue that they are wannabees, thus their bullshit tales are accepted as fact. Does this 99 % include PTSD counsellors? In many cases, it seems to, as most (not all but most) PTSD disability pensioners I've met have cashed in their wolf tickets for tax dollars. Anyone have any idea how much money is paid for PTSD anually? Anybody want to bet how much of it is legit, vs. how much is scam? Probably exceeds the amount Clinton's campaign took in in illegal contributions... and THAT's a lot! Now THAT would make a good grad student thesis.. or a PC busting expose!
